text: haey now thngai delke noam puok del brachheang towkean nork ( daoy niyeay tha) tae nih minmen chea karpit te ryy? puokke ban tb vinh tha pitmenhaey saum sbath nung mcheasa robsa puok yeung . trong mean bantoul tha dau che neah chaur puok anak phloksa nouv tearounakamm nih daoy sar te puok anak thleab ban brachheang choh
